OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FWarm during
OL,6,Fthe evening with some clear spells,
OL,7,Fbut periodically rather cloudy in the
OL,8,Fnorthwest, with spells of rain
OL,9,Fpossible here. Becoming generally
OL,10,Fdrier with clearer periods developing
OL,11,Fduring the early hours.
OL,12,
OL,13,CFriday:FMainly fine with sunny spells
OL,14,Fintially, but tending to becoming
OL,15,Fcloudier from the northwest through
OL,16,Fthe day, perhaps culminating in late
OL,17,Frain in the west. Very warm and humid.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
