OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fand damp for a time Saturday, but
OL,7,Fbecoming brighter with sunny spells
OL,8,Flater in the weekend, perhaps
OL,9,Ftriggering some thunderstorms on
OL,10,FMonday. Temperatures climbing, widely
OL,11,Fvery warm and humid.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
